{"pageProps":{"source":"<div class=\"space-y-4 whitespace-normal *:first:mt-0 *:last:mb-0\"><p><a class=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://doc.ubuntu-fr.org/ecryptfs\">eCryptfs</a> est un outil pour chiffrer un dossier.</p><h2>Installation</h2><p>Pour l&#x27;installer sur Debian ou Ubuntu :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">apt update &amp;&amp; apt install -y ecryptfs-utils\n</code></pre></div><h2>Initialisation</h2><p>Pour initialiser le répertoire <code>~/.Private</code> :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">ecryptfs-setup-private\n</code></pre></div><h2>Utilisation</h2><p>Pour monter le répertoire :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">ecryptfs-mount-private\n</code></pre></div><p>Pour démonter le répertoire :</p><div class=\"relative group\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"invisible group-hover:visible absolute top-0 right-0 rounded-md text-xs bg-gray-300 m-3 p-1.5 cursor-pointer leading-none\">Copier</button><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">ecryptfs-umount-private \n</code></pre></div></div>","isIndex":false,"file":"eCryptfs.md","fileName":"eCryptfs","title":"Chiffrer un dossier avec eCryptfs","comments":true,"permalink":"chiffrer-un-dossier-avec-ecryptfs","datePublished":"2021-06-27T19:19","dateUpdated":"2021-06-27T19:19","publish":true,"rss":true,"description":"Guide pour chiffrer un dossier avec eCryptfs sur Ubuntu ou Debian.","note":"54"},"__N_SSG":true}